      "text": "Sa a se Azizi. Azizi se poupe m' nan."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_03_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Mwen renmen Azizi paske li toujou ap souri."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_04_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Apre mwen, reveye mwen lave figi m'. Apre sa, mwen gade pou Azizi."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_05_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Lè m' jwenn Azizi, mwen bwose cheve li."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_06_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Lè m' manje manje matin, mwen bay Azizi manje."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_07_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Lè m' manje bagay dous, mwen bay Azizi youn."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_08_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Men, Azizi pa janm manje bagay dous. Mwen mande m' poukisa !"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_09_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Mwen mache nan lavironn ansent lan, poum ka keyi flè."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_10_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Mwen bay Azizi yon flè. Men, li pa janm di, « Mèsi dèske ou ban mwen li. >>"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_11_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Mwen lave Azizi pwòp anvan manman benyen m'."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_12_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Mwen abiye Azizi an wouj paske mwen renmen koulè wouj la."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f60d273ac-f12c-45a2-9f67-facba0b1119e%2fAzizi+poupe+a%2fASP_146_azizi_the_doll_1_Page_13_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Lè m' ale dòmi, mwen mete Azizi kouche bò kote m'."
